dct_description_sm: Subject: Map of the Minnesota Territory, divided into counties. Shows rivers, land plots and Indian reservations.

Originally bound in cover.; Cover title: Chapman's sectional map of Minnesota.; "Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1855 by Silas Chapman in the clerk's office of the District Court of the state of Wisconsin."
